    {
      "bookmarkId": "25791061_6_1088-1223",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1088-1223",
      "markText": "夏礼，吾能言之，杞不足征也；殷礼，吾能言之，宋不足征也。文献不足故也。足，则吾能征之矣。”(2)",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25791061&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1088&rangeEnd=1223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c15320c071898a55c15a971?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1088&rangeEnd=1223"
    },
